                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18010520-73-off398 t18010520-73-cd399"></join>, a cloth coat, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18010520-73-victim576" type="victimName">
                     John 
                     Edwards
                  <interp inst="t18010520-73-victim576" type="surname" value="Edwards"></interp>
